===Etymology 1===
From {{der|en|fro|querele}} (modern {{cog|fr|querelle}}), itself from {{der|en|la|querella|t=complaint}}, from {{m|la|queror|t=I lament, I complain}}.

Replaced {{cog|ang|sacan}} by 1340 as “ground for complaint”.

